(15743672, 'Slate Shadow Tennis Skirt', 'The Slate Shadow Tennis Skirt combines sporty elegance with classic sophistication. Crafted from lightweight, breathable fabric, this skirt offers freedom of movement on the court while keeping you cool and comfortable. Its subtle gray hue adds a touch of understated style, perfect for pairing with any tennis top or sports attire. Whether you\'re serving up aces or enjoying a casual match, the Slate Shadow Tennis Skirt ensures you look and feel your best with every swing.', 350, 'Womens', '45(2).png'),
(15743673, 'Earthy Elegance Pants', 'The Earthy Elegance Pants are a timeless wardrobe essential, offering both style and comfort in a rich brown hue. Crafted from high-quality fabric with a hint of stretch, these pants feature a tailored fit that flatters the silhouette while providing freedom of movement. Whether paired with a crisp shirt for a polished look or a casual tee for laid-back vibes, the Earthy Elegance Pants are perfect for any occasion, exuding sophistication and versatility.', 500, 'Mens', '49(2).png'),
(15743674, 'Breezy Blossom Mini Skirt', 'The Breezy Blossom Mini Skirt is a playful and flirty addition to your wardrobe, perfect for embracing sunny days with style. Crafted from lightweight fabric, this skirt features a flattering A-line silhouette that flows with every step. Its shorter length adds a touch of flirtation, while the vibrant floral pattern infuses your look with charm and energy. Whether paired with a crop top for a summer festival or a blouse for a casual outing, the Breezy Blossom Mini Skirt promises to elevate your ensemble with its effortless grace and femininity.', 389, 'Womens', '54(1).png');
